{"tid":913744,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"詠謙 詠謙佢一朝得志 （原曲︰周國腎－理性與感情）","createTime":"2018-11-23T15:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T07:44:15.000Z","uid":68884,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1808b8f56a1786540bffe507f2cf4eaaa94fabe5","tid":913744,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"詠謙&nbsp;詠謙佢一朝得志<br />\n詠謙&nbsp;詠謙佢不懂寫作&nbsp;亂試<br />\n每首歌堆砌字句全沒意義<br />\n詠謙&nbsp;詠謙放開手一試<br />\n詠謙&nbsp;詠謙佢癡Q咗線<br />\n歌詞&nbsp;騎呢修辭&nbsp;<br />\n令偉文亦覺得羞恥<br />\n<br />\n一首歌曲&nbsp;寫得再美好<br />\n歌手的音準感情再好<br />\n要是涉及你&nbsp;都很糟糕<br />\n<br />\n如流行歌曲加上李力持<br />\n如蓮蓉屎沾污了靚泳池<br />\n無能何必假裝高深故意<br />\n還越來越見自負做幕前<br />\n首首歌有你份詞<br />\n還維護廣東歌 哪個願意<br />\n陳姓詠謙這個毒瘤確實唔掂<br />\n你填詞不過二線<br />\n<br />\n陳詠謙我屌你老母，年中浪費咗幾多歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6b2a44643bd1901396120fb9fc63807b39abb5","tid":913744,"uid":200606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"二線算抬舉佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2431f9fa0a58017cb519325520302a316cd7dd16","tid":913744,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6b2a44643bd1901396120fb9fc63807b39abb5","tid":913744,"uid":200606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"二線算抬舉佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"要比番少少面人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a706ded30af1310d8b2de82a0d1e907f8d0aa8","tid":913744,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"佢鬼有二線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 